# expressivity artifacts (host on GH release/HF, do not commit big binaries)
qwen3-tts-1.7b-expr/
# The big .expr weight-deltas are hosted on HF (gabrione/qwen3-tts-italian-expr) and fetched
# on demand by download_assets.sh (sha256-verified against presets/expr/MANIFEST.md, which IS
# tracked). HF is the durable backup now, so we no longer track any .expr in git — this also
# closes the loss-risk behind the 2026-06-15 regression (validated .expr lost with no backup).
presets/expr/*.expr
!training/expressivity-lora/*.py
# Local-only GPU-box trainer/sync scripts (private LAN) — must come AFTER the *.py
# re-include above so they stay ignored (they are pulled to the box, not for the public repo).
training/expressivity-lora/gpu_*
training/expressivity-lora/sync_*to_gpu.sh
# local training data (prep outputs: wav24k + manifests + codes) — never commit
training/expressivity-lora/data*/

